com.enhancell.remote

Class Device.DeviceStates

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.enhancell.remote.Device.DeviceStates
  • Enclosing interface:
    Device

    public static final class Device.DeviceStates
extends java.lang.Object
    DeviceStates class contains the state flags for describing the UE's state. To check for a particular state a bitwise AND operation should be performed.
